  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>. This exploration vessel is configured with <span class=\"name name-technology\">Economy</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Conflict Scanners</span>, for remotely probing system data.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，这艘探索飞船装备<span class=\"name name-technology\">经济</span>与<span class=\"name name-technology\">冲突扫描仪</span>，能够远程获取星系数据。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>。這艘探索太空船搭載了<span class=\"name name-technology\">經濟</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">衝突掃描器</span>，能夠遠端探測星系資料。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
